@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About BigCalculator</PageTitle>

<h1>About BigCalculator</h1>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>Project Information</h2>
        <p>
            BigCalculator is a high-precision calculator built using the BigFloat library. It provides
            accurate calculations with arbitrary precision, supporting various number bases and advanced
            mathematical operations.
        </p>

        <h3>Contributors</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Ryan Scott White - Project Creator and Developer</li>
            <li>
                <a href="https://www.anthropic.com/claude" target="_blank">Claude 3.7 from Anthropic</a> - 
                AI assistant that helped with development, code generation, and documentation
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Technologies</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <a href="https://github.com/SunsetQuest/BigFloat" target="_blank">BigFloat Library</a> - 
                High-precision floating-point arithmetic library
            </li>
            <li>Blazor WebAssembly - For running calculations directly in the browser</li>
            <li>.NET 9 - Modern framework for building web applications</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
